sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant User
  participant Main as src/main.rs
  participant Update as update::mod
  participant Check as update::check
  participant Network as update::network
  participant Checksum as update::checksum
  participant Archive as update::archive
  participant Install as update::install
  participant Post as update::post_install

  User->>Main: azork update --check or azork update
  Main->>Update: run_update_with(check_only)
  alt check only
    Update->>Update: resolve_latest_update
    Update->>Network: fetch_latest_release
    Network-->>Update: GithubRelease and assets
    Update->>Update: normalize_tag, is_newer, select_asset
    Update-->>User: newer available or already latest
  else install
    Update->>Update: do_update
    Update->>Network: fetch_latest_release
    Network-->>Update: resolved asset and checksum URL
    Update->>Check: write_last_check best effort
    Update->>Install: download_and_replace(resolved)
    Install->>Network: download archive and checksum asset
    Install->>Checksum: verify_sha256
    Checksum-->>Install: pass or ChecksumMismatch
    Install->>Archive: extract_binary traversal-safe
    Archive-->>Install: extracted azork binary
    Install->>Install: atomically replace current executable
    Install->>Post: write installed-version stamp
    Update-->>User: updated or error exit code
  end
